{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people would stand there and-- and shiver, rightfully, and say, oh my god, now we are going to get the pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is all we need.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can't last anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these-- these people with that attitude, of course, had a problem.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and while it's understandable, I'm not trying to criticize it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my brother and I were watching each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we would-- we were not allowed to run around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you could stomp on the spot if you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we would rub each other's back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- and then we would say, hey, listen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Isn't this wonderful?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The snow, the hot bath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Isn't it just like the Swedish baths are?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is supposed to be healthy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that we'll be healthy, and that will be helping us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People around us looked like as if we were nuts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they-- they went, hey, what are these guys talking?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so this is one of the things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then eventually, it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because these guards that-- guards that handed out the clothing had their drinks and-- and their cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would take all their time, would slap each others on the shoulder in their big fat coats, and took all the time in the world to hand the clothing out.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to give you a little scene of part of survival, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyways, as the Russians came closer, now towards the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am talking by now it's January, beginning of January, 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Russians from the East had thrown the Germans back, finally, further and further towards German-- German soil, towards Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course they came towards Auschwitz, which is located in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
